Standard and Poor's Corp said itupgraded Phelps Dodge Corp's senior debt to BB-plus from BB andpreference stock to BB-minus from B-plus.    About 400 mln dlrs of debt and preference stock isoutstanding.    Continuing cost cutting in its copper operations hassignificantly enhanced the firm's competitive position, S and Psaid. It added that the acquisition of Columbian Chemical Cohas broadened Phelps Dodge's earnings base. Reuter&#3;